<h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0;">Order Update</h2>
<p>Hi {{fullname}},</p>
<p>An item from your order <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong> has been updated.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f1f5f9; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b;">Product: {{productName}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #4f46e5; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">Status: {{statusLabel}}</p>
</div>

{{#if trackingNumber}}
<p>You can track your package using the tracking number below:</p>
<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase;">Tracking Number</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;">{{trackingNumber}}</p>
    {{#if carrier}}
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">Carrier: {{carrier}}</p>
    {{/if}}
</div>
{{/if}}

<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/account/orders/{{orderId}}" class="btn">View Full Order Status</a>
</div>
<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">Thank you for shopping with Zapify!</p>
